query: SELECT s.id, s.name, s.totalDistance, s.totalRides, s.userId, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ridingRecords r WHERE r.scooterId = s.id AND r.userId = s.userId) as actualRides, (SELECT COALESCE(SUM(r.distance), 0) FROM ridingRecords r WHERE r.scooterId = s.id AND r.userId = s.userId) as actualDistance FROM scooters s WHERE s.totalDistance = 0 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ridingRecords r WHERE r.scooterId = s.id AND r.userId = s.userId) > 0 LIMIT 10;
